@startuml 17-search-pagination
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Search Pagination (Infinite Scroll)

actor User
participant "SearchResultsPage" as UI
participant "IntersectionObserver" as IO
participant "SearchApi" as SVC
participant "POST /api/search" as API

UI --> User: page 1 rendered (50 rows, nextPage=2)
User -> UI: scroll toward bottom
IO -> UI: sentinel intersected\n(<=200px from bottom)
UI -> SVC: search({ q, sort, page:2 })
SVC -> API: POST
API --> SVC: 200 { results:[50], nextPage:3 }
SVC --> UI: append rows
UI --> User: 100 rendered (virtualized ~80 in DOM)

User -> UI: continue scroll
IO -> UI: sentinel intersects again
UI -> SVC: search({ page:3 })
SVC -> API: POST
API --> SVC: 200 { results:[20], nextPage:null }
SVC --> UI: append rows
UI --> User: "End of results"

@enduml
